graph TD
    A[User Request] --> B{Supervisor / Orchestrator}
    
    subgraph Multi-Agent System
    B -->|Routes Task| C[Writer Agent]
    C -->|Returns Draft| B
    
    B -->|Routes Task| D[Compliance Agent]
    D -->|Returns Feedback| B
    
    B -->|Routes Task| E[SEO Agent]
    E -->|Returns Keywords| B
    end
    
    B -->|Decides Task is Complete| F[Final Output Aggregation]
    
    %% Note styling
    classDef supervisor fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;
    class B supervisor;
    
    classDef worker fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    class C,D,E worker;
